专门为专业调色师设计的显示器来说非常值得尊敬。为此，颜色精度被校准为 Delta E &lt; 1，它是真正的 10 位面板，可提供数十亿种颜色。为了验证这一点，它甚至还配备了 X-rite i1 Display Pro 色彩校准器，通常单独出售，价格约为 500 美元。</p><p>除了该型号之外，华硕现在还生产了几种亮度稍差且价格较低的变体，即 4,180 美元的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQmWPCyLh1cJJUlw-YLdKwyg1UntkbH0_Mqqpea3RUH6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB088MKPYD4%2Fref%3Das_li_ss_tl" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B088MKPYD4/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=buyersguide2022-20&amp;language=en_US" class="rapid-with-clickid">PA32UCX-PK</a> （加上功能略有不同的 -P 和 -K 变体），提供 1,200 尼特的亮度和 60Hz（不包括120Hz）刷新率。其他方面的规格几乎相同。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/how-to-buy-a-monitor-143000069.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/how-to-buy-a-monitor-143000069.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 007f96e7-0ec9-3a79-a6ae-d5271643cdbd</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 19:05:15 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691610522</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T19:48:50+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[news]]></category><category><![CDATA[refreshrate]]></category><category><![CDATA[entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[HDR]]></category><category><![CDATA[4K]]></category><category><![CDATA[display]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[resolution]]></category><category><![CDATA[contentcreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category><![CDATA[monitors]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicEquipment,Instruments&Components]]></category><c